{"header":{"word":"מִזְרָח","entry":2731,"letter":"ז","strongs":4217,"page":280},"definitions":[{"title":"Def","body":" &#134; [[מִזְרָח]] ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"n.[m.]","body":" place of sunrise, east&#8212;abs. &#180;[[מ]] Jos 11:3 + 21 t.; cstr. [[מִזְרַח]] Nu 21:10 + 19 t., c. [[ה]] loc. [[מִזְרָ֫חָה]] Ex 27:13 + 28 t., cstr. [[מִזְרְחָה]] De 4:41, Jos 12:1, Ju Jdg 21:19 (not in Gn Lv Sa Ez etc.);&#8212;","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"1.","body":" sunrise always of quarter of the heavens = east [[שׁמשׁ]]([[ה]]) &#180;[[מ]] Nu 21:11 (P), De 4:41, De 4:47, Jos 1:15, Jos 12:1, Jos 13:5 (all D), Jos 19:12, Jos 19:27, Jos 19:34 (all P), Ju Jdg 20:43, Jdg 21:19, 2Ki 10:33, Is 41:25, Is 45:6, Is 59:19, cf. [[שׁמשׁ לארץ]] &#180;[[מ]] Ju Jdg 11:18; [[שׁמשׁ וְעַד־מְבוֹאוֹ]] &#180;[[מִמִּז]] Ps 50:1, Ps 113:3, Mal 1:11; more often ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"2.","body":" without [[שֶׁמֶשׁ]]: ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"a.","body":" the east &#180;[[כִּרְחׂק מ]] [[מִמַּעֲרָבָ]] Ps 103:12. ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"b.","body":" &#180;[[מִמּ]] from the east Is 41:2, Is 43:5 (opp. [[מִמַּעֲרָב]]), Is 46:11, Da 11:44 (+ [[מִצַּפוֹן]]); &#180;[[מִמּ]] [[וּמִמַּעֲרָבָ מִצָּפוֹן וּמִיׇּם]] Ps 107:3. ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"c.","body":" to or toward the place of sunrise, to the east, eastward: (1) [[מִוְרָ֫חָה]] Nu 32:19 (P), De 3:17, De 3:27 (&#180;[[יׇ֫מָּה וְחָםפ֫וֹנׇה וְתֵימָ֫נׇה וּמ]]), De 4:49, Jos 11:8, Jos 16:1 (JE), Jos 12:1, Jos 12:3, Jos 12:3, Jos 13:8 (all D), v:Jos 13:27, v:Jos 13:32, Jos 16:5, Jos 18:7, Jos 20:8 (all P), 1Ch 9:18, 1Ch 26:14; &#8214;[[קֵ֫דְמָה]] Nu 3:38, Jos 19:13 (both P) Je 31:40; &#8214;[[חָםפ֫וֹנׇה]], [[יׇ֫מָּה]], [[נֶ֫גְבָּה]] 1Ki 7:25, cf. Jos 16:6 (P) 1Ch 26:17; + [[קֵ֫דְמָה]] Ex 27:13, Ex 38:13, Nu 2:3, Nu 34:15 (all P); [[מִקֶּדֶם]] Zec 14:4 (opp. [[יׇ֫מָּה]]); (2) [[מִזְ רָךְ]] (without [[ה]] loc.), [[יׇ֫מָּה חָםפ֫וֹנׇה וׇנֶ֫גְבָּה]] &#180;[[מ]] 1Ch 9:24, cf. Ne 12:37; [[לַמִּזְבֵּחַ]] &#180;[[מ]] 2Ch 5:12; (3) &#180;[[לַמִּז]] 1Ch 5:9, 1Ch 7:28 (opp. [[לַמַּעֲרָב]]) 1Ch 12:16 (so Baer; v:1Ch 12:15 van d. H; opp. id.), 1Ch 26:17 (+ [[לַצָּפ֫וֹנׇה]], [[לַנֶּ֫גְבָּה]]), Ne 3:26; [[לַמִּזְרָ֫חָה]] 2Ch 31:14; (4) &#180;[[אֶל־הַמּ]] Da 8:9 (+ [[אֶל־הַנֶּגֶב]], [[אֶל־הַצֶּבִָי]]); (5) [[מִיׇּם עָד־יׇם וּמִצָּפוֹן עַד־מִזְ רָךְ]] Am 8:12. ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"d.","body":" (on) the east side of, cstr. [[קְחֵה מִזְרַה יְרִיחוֹ]] Jos 4:19 (P); also c. [[לְמִזְרַח הַנׇּ֑יְא לְ]] 1Ch 4:39, [[הַיַּרְדֵּן]] &#180;[[לְמ]] 1Ch 6:63; c. [[מִן]], &#180;[[מִמִּז]] Jos 11:3 (opp. [[מִיׇּם]]) cf. Jos 17:10 (+ [[מצָּפוֹן]]; both JE), also Jos 16:6 (P). ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"e.","body":" after a cstr. [[לגלעד]] &#180;[[עַל־כָּל־פְּנֵי מ]] 1Ch 5:10; &#180;[[רְחוֹב הַמּ]] 2Ch 29:4; &#180;[[שַׁעַר הַמּ]] Ne 3:29; &#180;[[אֶרֶץ מ]] Zec 8:7 (opp. [[ארץ מְבוֹא]] [[הַשֶּׁמֶשׁ]]).\r","content":"definition","show":"block"}],"notes":"","etymology":[],"morphology":[]}